*CoderDojo Zen*
Initial release is to a basic Dojo listing manager.
Plans to enhance and add features down the line

*Zen is built on and uses: *
* CodeIgnitor http://codeigniter.com/
* Tank Auth http://www.konyukhov.com/soft/tank_auth/
* Twitter Bootstrap http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/

*Sensitive information in files: *
* application/config/database.php (Orchestra DB login)
* application/config/email.php (SendGrid's SMTP password & username)
* application/config/tank_auth.php (reCaptcha keys)
(make sure we deal with this prior to open sourcing)

